description:
An official weather app by Gismeteo.

Key features:
— accurate daily and hourly weather forecasts;
— weather at your favorite locations and all over the world;
— nearby locations search;
— beautiful and simple interface;
— offline mode (showing earlier downloaded data).

We’ll gladly receive your feedback and suggestions. Feel free to contact us at: apps@gismeteo.com

Hi Weather is a gadget app that displays the current weather and the weather for the next few days.

Using our app, you can more conveniently plan your itinerary for work, travel, etc. We have a wealth of features to meet any of your needs.

Function:

- Current weather: weather, temperature, humidity, visibility, atmospheric pressure, precipitation probability, storm, storm, sleet, etc. at the current time;

- Future weather: Provides weather forecast for the next 5 days, which also includes temperature, humidity, visibility, atmospheric pressure, precipitation probability, storms, storms, sleet, etc.;

- Sunrise and sunset: predict daily local sunrise and sunset times;

- Multiple unit conversions: Freely switch between Celsius and Fahrenheit temperatures, different wind speed units, and freely change according to your needs at any time;

- Weather conditions in multiple places: global city query, you can search and add the cities you want according to your needs, and keep track of weather conditions in multiple places at any time;

Thanks for using our Hi Weather!
